02:24.999 --> 02:27.917
<i>He killed our friend.
She was a cop.</i>

02:27.952 --> 02:30.419
Then you came a long way for nothing.

02:30.455 --> 02:33.745
Oh, fuck.
I blame you for this.

02:40.515 --> 02:45.634
This woman you say Chayton killed,
what did she do to him?

02:46.086 --> 02:47.303
