02:48.856 --> 02:53.309
- Then why would he take her life?
- 'Cause he's a fucking psychopath.

02:53.361 --> 02:56.321
There was a time when you
people would have called him

02:56.322 --> 02:59.281
- a wild savage instead.
- Yeah, that sounds about right.

02:59.317 --> 03:04.653
