Hit that motherfucker.

05:39.810 --> 05:42.194
- Hit that motherfucker.
- Boys, let's up the ante.

05:42.230 --> 05:44.146
Let's get some real shit up in here.

05:44.148 --> 05:46.732
<i>Yeah! Yeah! Yeah!</i>

