- God damn it.

39:38.481 --> 39:41.232
What do you think she
would have wanted, huh?

39:45.438 --> 39:48.573
I'm not going back
to Banshee without you.

39:50.693 --> 39:53.194
Gotta finish what you started.

39:54.864 --> 39:57.248
Even if I've got to kick your
ass all the way back there myself.

40:02.372 --> 40:04.705
I'm not leaving without you.

40:08.044 --> 40:10.211
Are you done?

40:12.215 --> 40:14.382
I think so.

40:17.186 --> 40:19.136
Come on.

40:34.320 --> 40:37.572
<i>In the name of the Lord and the Church,</i>

40:37.624 --> 40:41.409
<i>we extend to you the hand of fellowship.</i>

40:41.461 --> 40:45.463
<i>"I am He who blots
out your transgressions</i>

40:45.548 --> 40:46.964
<i>for my own sake</i>

40:47.000 --> 40:50.084
<i>and remembers your sins no more."</i>

40:51.638 --> 40:56.090
<i>Rise up and be ye a faithful
member of the Church.</i>

41:09.155 --> 41:11.405
In youth we learn.

41:11.441 --> 41:13.574
In age we understand.

41:14.861 --> 41:17.194
This belonged to your mother.

41:19.165 --> 41:21.248
Thank you, Father.

41:23.086 --> 41:24.335
Thank you.

41:42.722 --> 41:44.555
Kai.

41:47.810 --> 41:50.478
Let's go.

42:43.916 --> 42:47.034
<i>Bacon burger.
Cheeseburger.</i>

