- Hey.
- Hello, Carrie.

43:17.734 --> 43:22.403
- Jesus. What happened to you?
- I got robbed.

43:22.405 --> 43:25.906
- Doug, are you okay?
- I will be.

43:25.908 --> 43:30.911
- Did you call the cops?
- No, I'll be handling this myself.

43:30.963 --> 43:33.464
Maybe you can help.

43:33.499 --> 43:38.252
I understand your father was
no stranger to illegal behavior.

43:39.972 --> 43:43.257
