the nuances of the criminal mind.

43:43.309 --> 43:47.344
My father and I had
a complicated relationship.

43:47.396 --> 43:50.848
- I doubt I'd be much help.
- Okay.

43:52.101 --> 43:55.686
- I'd like some more water, please.
- Of course.

