with a gentle touch.

45:10.096 --> 45:12.677
The approach was simple, elegant.

45:12.678 --> 45:14.398
<i>The work of a professional.</i>

45:19.355 --> 45:21.572
Are you sure I can't
get you anything else?

45:21.607 --> 45:23.240
Not today.

45:25.328 --> 45:28.779
<i>The one I haven't figured out
is the one you fought in the tunnel.</i>

45:28.831 --> 45:30.581
He was well trained.

45:30.616 --> 45:33.284
<i>Lethal, but a little rusty.</i>

45:33.336 --> 45:35.419
<i>He allowed his enemy to live</i>

45:35.454 --> 45:39.039
